descriptionHtml:
This is only Brighter and more colorful textures for the children\'s clothes.
I just love having bright colors in my games.
You can do with this whatever you want.
I hope you like it - If you don\'t it\'s Okay - we all like different things!

For Andrew who loves The Elder Scrolls.

Please note that the Armor the Character is wearing is not included in this Pack. I was only testing some textures and it was the only Screenshot I currently have with children in it.
author: JackalDeMon
